<reference id="dlentry" xml:lang="en-us">
<title><xmlelement>dlentry</xmlelement></title>
<shortdesc>The <xmlelement>dlentry</xmlelement> element groups a single entry in a definition list
      (<xmlelement>dl</xmlelement>). The <xmlelement>dlentry</xmlelement> element includes a term
      (<xmlelement>dt</xmlelement>) and one or more definitions or descriptions
      (<xmlelement>dd</xmlelement>) of that term.</shortdesc>
